The paper discusses the use of an AI-powered chatbot to conduct conversational surveys, which involves natural language processing and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The chatbot interprets free-text responses, which involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and the chatbot itself is powered by AI (cs.AI). The study also involves analyzing the quality of responses, which could fall under cybernetics (cs.CY) or social and information networks (cs.SI).
